org.phoenixbioinformatics.api.db.api

Interface ISubscriptionDescription

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto>, com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto, com.poesys.db.dto.IObserver, com.poesys.db.dto.ISubject, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSubscriptionDescription, AbstractSubscriptionDescriptionProxy, SubscriptionDescription, SubscriptionDescriptionProxy

    public interface ISubscriptionDescription
extends com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto

    A data-access layer data-transfer-object interface for the SubscriptionDescription. The data-transfer-object class and proxy class implement this interface, as does the business-layer data-transfer-object class.

    A collection of descriptive texts to display for a particular kind of subscription; a partner may have any number of such texts to display in different named contexts

    Stereotypes:

    • CompositeKey
    • Persistent

    Class is read/write: true

    Author:
    Poesys/DB Cartridge
